eft class=m><span class=title> Upgraded mob damage</span><hr size=1> we were using this zone to exp a bit and the 10/18 patch changed that lol.<br>
<br>
The standard lawn trash mobs (e.g. shrooms, outcasts, razors etc) now hit from over 220 max, making single group forays much more difficult.<br>
<br>
I'd imagine this was to discourage aoe groups (back to kunark with you!=) but multi mobs pulls are pretty ugly now.<br>
<br>
Honestly, the exp mod seemed to get bumped up as well such that the exp per kill is significantly higher but it's kind of a shame that yet another &quot;broken group&quot; (Anything that breaks from the tried and true Healer, Tank, Slower/mezzer combo) friendly zone poofed =/<br>
<br>
<br>
Back to fungal for those post raid exp groups I guess<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Cheers!<br>
